          "text": "Positive\nNikolsky’s sign\nFebrile\nStaphylococcal scalded skin syndrome\n(children)\nToxic epidermal necrolysis\n/\nSJS\n(adults)\nAfebrile\nToxic epidermal necrolysis\nNegative\nNikolsky’s sign\nFebrile\nToxic shock syndrome\nKawasaki disease\nScarlet fever\nDRESS syndrome\nCellulitis\nAcute generalized exanthematous pustulosis\nAfebrile\nAlcohol intoxication\nAnaphylaxis\nCellulitis\nDermatitis\n(multiple types)\nDrug rash\nErysipelas\nErythema multiforme\nExfoliative erythroderma\nScombroid\nVancomycin infusion reaction",
