    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "PCR for toxin if available\nCBC -\nleukocytosis\n, though normal WBC level oftenly\nESR elevation\nMonitor electrolytes, renal function closely in severe disease\nBlood cultures variably positive (more often pos in adults)\nCXR\nto rule out pneumonia",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
